Rating: 3
this was great and so easy to make. it took no time at all to make the sauce. Its got great flavor and very spicy especially if you do in fact use the chili sauce. I used 2 different thai chili sauces that I had on hand--a garlic chili sauce and a sweet chilli sauce (I didn't have enough of one so I combined them). it was really good. if you like spicy this is a good one! we'll be using this again and again.

